#: ../../glossary/useful_information/howto_fading_inout_kdenlive_titles.rst:13
msgid "How to fading in-out Kdenlive titles"
msgstr "Kako odtemniti in zatemniti naslove Kdenlive"

#: ../../glossary/useful_information/howto_fading_inout_kdenlive_titles.rst:15
msgid ""
"In this short *HOWTO* video, we show you how to (smoothly) fade in and out "
"Kdenlive titles over a video clip, fading from and to transparency. The key "
"to success is to use a **Composite & Transform** transition with keyframes "
"(**Affine** and **Composite** will work too). **Don’t use** the Fade from/to "
"Black effects though, as these effects remove the title transparency "
"information."
msgstr ""
"V tem kratkem *pojasnilnem* videoposnetku vam pokažemo, kako (gladko) "
"odtemniti in zatemniti naslove Kdenlive preko video posnetka, ki se odstemni "
"in zatemni v prosojnost. Ključ do uspeha je uporaba prehoda **Sestava in "
"preoblikovanje** s ključnimi sličicami (delovala bosta tudi **Afino** in "
"**Sestavljeno**). **Ne uporabljajte** učinkov Zatemni/Odtemni, saj ti učinki "
"odstranijo informacije o prosojnosti naslova."

#: ../../glossary/useful_information/howto_fading_inout_kdenlive_titles.rst:23
msgid "Notes"
msgstr "Opombe"

#: ../../glossary/useful_information/howto_fading_inout_kdenlive_titles.rst:25
msgid "These are the individual steps shown in this HOWTO video:"
msgstr "To so posamezni koraki, prikazani v tem videu:"

#: ../../glossary/useful_information/howto_fading_inout_kdenlive_titles.rst:27
msgid "Add a Composite & Transform transition to the title clip."
msgstr "V naslovni posnetek dodajte prehod Sestavi in preoblikuj."

#: ../../glossary/useful_information/howto_fading_inout_kdenlive_titles.rst:28
msgid ""
"First keyframe: set the opacity to 0%. This marks the beginning of the fade "
"in (ramp up)."
msgstr ""
"Prva ključna sličica: nastavite prekrivnost na 0 %. To označuje začetek "
"odtemnitve v (navzgor)."

#: ../../glossary/useful_information/howto_fading_inout_kdenlive_titles.rst:30
msgid ""
"Second keyframe: add a new keyframe where you want the title to be fully "
"faded in, set the opacity to 100%. Set the type of the keyframe to Linear."
msgstr ""
"Druga ključna sličica: dodajte novo ključno sličico, kjer želite, da je "
"naslov v celoti prikazan, nastavite prekrivnost na 100 %. Nastavite vrsto "
"ključne sličice na linearno."

#: ../../glossary/useful_information/howto_fading_inout_kdenlive_titles.rst:30
msgid ""
"The rationale to set this keyframe to Linear is that otherwise Kdenlive "
"(MLT) calculates a smooth curve fitting to the previous and following "
"keyframe, causing the opacity value to overshoot. With a maximum possible "
"opacity of 100% you won’t notice. However, when you use a maximum opacity of "
"less than 100%, then this overshooting may become visible."
msgstr ""
"Razlog za nastavitev te ključne sličice na linearno je, da Kdenlive (MLT) "
"sicer izračuna gladko krivuljo, ki se prilega prejšnji in naslednji ključni "
"sličici, kar povzroča, da vrednost prekrivnosti preseže najvišjo možno "
"vrednost. Z največjo možno prekrivnostjo 100 % tega res ne boste opazili. Če "
"pa uporabljate največjo prekrivnost, ki je manjša od 100 %, se lahko to "
"opazi."

#: ../../glossary/useful_information/howto_fading_inout_kdenlive_titles.rst:31
msgid ""
"Ensure that the first keyframe is Smooth. You can only adjust the type of "
"the first keyframes after you’ve added a second keyframe."
msgstr ""
"Zagotovite, da je prva ključna sličica Gladka. Vrsto prvih ključnih sličic "
"lahko prilagodite šele, ko dodate drugo ključno sličico."

#: ../../glossary/useful_information/howto_fading_inout_kdenlive_titles.rst:32
msgid ""
"Third keyframe: add another keyframe near the end where you want to start "
"fading out the title. Leave the opacity at 100%. Set the keyframe type to "
"Smooth."
msgstr ""
"Tretja ključna sličica: dodajte še eno ključno sličico blizu konca, kjer "
"želite začeti zatemnjevati naslov. Pustite prekrivnost pri 100 %. Nastavite "
"vrsto ključne sličice na Gladko."

#: ../../glossary/useful_information/howto_fading_inout_kdenlive_titles.rst:33
msgid "Fourth keyframe: add a final keyframe, where you set the opacity to 0%."
msgstr ""
"Četrta ključna sličica: dodajte končno ključno sličico, kjer nastavite "
"prekrivnost na 0 %."

#: ../../glossary/useful_information/howto_fading_inout_kdenlive_titles.rst:35
msgid "Done."
msgstr "Končano."

#: ../../glossary/useful_information/howto_fading_inout_kdenlive_titles.rst:37
msgid ""
"In case you are scratching your head now, why this mixture of smooth and "
"linear interpolated keyframes? Then head over to our new article on :ref:"
"`the_smooth_keyframe_interpolation`."
msgstr ""
"Ali se zdaj praskate po glavi, zakaj ta mešanica gladkih in linearnih "
"interpoliranih ključnih sličic? Potem si oglejte naš novi članek, tema je :"
"ref:`the_smooth_keyframe_interpolation`."
